        <prompt>What was the significance of the "Black Friday" uprising in Louisiana?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">A failed attempt by African Americans to defend voting rights</option>
            <option letter="b">An economic protest</option>
            <option letter="c">A labor strike</option>
            <option letter="d">A military conflict</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The Black Friday uprising was a failed attempt by African Americans to defend their voting rights against violent suppression in Louisiana.</explanation>
