        <prompt>What was the purpose of the "Uniform Militia Act"?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">To create white-controlled state militias</option>
            <option letter="b">To protect African Americans</option>
            <option letter="c">To support federal troops</option>
            <option letter="d">To enforce civil rights</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The Uniform Militia Act allowed Southern states to create white-controlled militias that were often used to intimidate African American voters.</explanation>
